<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Test Available: {{testTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .test-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        
        .test-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .test-details {
            display: grid;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            width: 120px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #4b5563;
        }
        
        .due-date {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .due-date p {
            color: #92400e;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .test-info {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .test-title {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .detail-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 5px;
            }
            
            .detail-label {
                width: auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìã New Test Available</h1>
            <p>You have been assigned a new test</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello{{#if recipientName}} {{recipientName}}{{/if}},
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                üéØ Great news! {{#if instructorName}}{{instructorName}}{{else}}Your instructor{{/if}} believes you're ready for your next challenge. This isn't just a test - it's your chance to showcase the knowledge you've gained and prove to yourself how much you've grown. Every question is an opportunity to demonstrate your expertise and take another confident step forward.
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Why this test matters:</strong> This assessment has been carefully designed to validate your understanding and identify areas where you excel. It's not about finding what you don't know - it's about celebrating what you do know and guiding your continued growth.
            </div>
            
            <div class="test-info">
                <div class="test-title">{{testTitle}}</div>
                
                <div class="test-details">
                    {{#if testDescription}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Description:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{testDescription}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Due Date:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{formatDate dueDate 'long'}}</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    {{#if duration}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Duration:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{duration}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    {{#if instructorName}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Instructor:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{instructorName}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="due-date">
                <p>‚è∞ Due: {{formatDate dueDate 'long'}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{testUrl}}" class="cta-button">Start Test</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Set yourself up for success:</strong>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Find a quiet, comfortable space where you can focus fully</li>
                    <li>Ensure you have a stable internet connection for the best experience</li>
                    <li>Take your time - rushing rarely leads to your best work</li>
                    <li>Trust your preparation - you know more than you think you do</li>
                    <li>Remember our support team is here if you need any technical help</li>
                    <li>Submit before the deadline to avoid any last-minute stress</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                We're cheering you on! This test is just another step in your learning journey, and we have complete confidence in your abilities. Remember, every challenge you overcome makes you stronger and more capable. You've got this! üåü
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>
                {{companyName}} | 
                {{#if unsubscribeUrl}}<a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a>{{/if}}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 